column5: Has anyone had their eggs taken from them at the border? Are they even asking about eggs?
I went across last month just as the egg scare was starting. No questions about eggs. ATF - that was about it.
cross the boarder may times no one ever asked about eggs, firearms, booze,tabaco yes, as for eggs i like mine over easy homefries toast and bacon,coffee
I like mine over easy too and also in an omelet with cheese and ham and a side of home fries and sausage links or patties
